Package java111.project5

Class ShippedOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • java111.project5.OrderProcess
      • java111.project5.ShippedOrder
  • public class ShippedOrder
extends OrderProcess
    The ShippedOrder class represents an order with optional shipping.

    This class is part of Project 5 - Part 2

    Shipping charge calculation:

    • 1-3 items: $1.50
    • 4-6 items: $3.00
    • 7-9 items: $6.00
    • 10+ items: $7.00
    Since:
    12/7/24
